---
import { Eye, Scale } from 'lucide-svelte';
---

<div class="slide slide-ethics swiper-slide">
  <div class="slide-background"></div>

  <div class="slide-content">
    <div class="slide-header">
      <h2>Riesgos Éticos</h2>
      <p class="subtitle">Dilemas morales en la era digital</p>
    </div>

    <div class="ethics-container">
      <div class="ethics-visual">
        <div class="ethics-icon">
          <Eye size={80} />
        </div>
        <p class="ethics-label">Vigilancia y Privacidad</p>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline">
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>Recopilación de datos</h3>
            <p>Sistemas de IA recopilan información personal masivamente</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>Perfilado discriminatorio</h3>
            <p>Creación de perfiles que pueden ser discriminatorios</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>Falta de consentimiento</h3>
            <p>Los usuarios muchas veces desconocen cómo se usan sus datos</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="quote-box">
      <p class="quote-text">"La privacidad no es un derecho que se negocia, es un derecho fundamental humano."</p>
      <p class="quote-author">— UNESCO</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .slide {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    overflow: hidden;
    background-color: var(--color-base-dark);
    padding: var(--spacing-2xl);
  }

  .slide-background {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(30, 58, 138, 0.4) 0%, transparent 50%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 100% 0%, rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.1) 0%, transparent 60%);
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .slide-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 1000px;
  }

  .slide-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2xl);
    animation: fadeIn 0.6s ease-out;
  }

  .slide-header h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    color: var(--color-accent-bright);
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.25rem);
    color: rgba(250, 249, 246, 0.7);
  }

  .ethics-container {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;
    gap: var(--spacing-2xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2xl);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .ethics-visual {
    text-align: center;
    animation: slideLeft 0.6s ease-out;
  }

  @keyframes slideLeft {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateX(-40px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateX(0);
    }
  }

  .ethics-icon {
    color: var(--color-electric);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .ethics-label {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: rgba(250, 249, 246, 0.85);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .timeline {
    animation: slideRight 0.6s ease-out;
  }

  @keyframes slideRight {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateX(40px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateX(0);
    }
  }

  .timeline-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--spacing-lg);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
    padding-left: var(--spacing-xl);
    position: relative;
  }

  .timeline-item::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 30px;
    width: 2px;
    height: calc(100% - 20px);
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--color-electric), transparent);
  }

  .timeline-item:last-child::before {
    display: none;
  }

  .timeline-marker {
    position: absolute;
    left: -8px;
    top: 8px;
    width: 16px;
    height: 16px;
    background: var(--color-electric);
    border: 3px solid var(--color-base-dark);
    border-radius: 50%;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .timeline-content h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--color-accent-bright);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .timeline-content p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: rgba(250, 249, 246, 0.75);
  }

  .quote-box {
    background: rgba(30, 58, 138, 0.3);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-electric);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: var(--spacing-2xl);
    text-align: center;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease-out 0.3s both;
  }

  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(20px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  .quote-text {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-neutral-light);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .quote-author {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--color-electric);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .slide {
      padding: var(--spacing-xl);
    }

    .ethics-container {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--spacing-xl);
    }

    .timeline {
      margin-top: var(--spacing-xl);
    }
  }
</style>
